<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/mar/08/">&#x27a0;</a> March 8, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Citizens Bank&#8217;s new logo</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/6159542/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Citizens Bank&#8217;s new logo" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/3/6159542_d92cfc3eee_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Looks <a href="http://www.royalbankofscotland.com/" rel="nofollow">somewhat familiar</a>, reminding me of my student days when the RBoS made my penniless days miserable.  I wish Bank of Scotland or Clydesdale owned a local bank.  I'd join in a flash!</p>
        </p>

